com.kt.explibs.warp.io.serial
类 SerialFlowWriter

java.lang.Object
  com.kt.explibs.warp.io.serial.SerialFlowWriter

public class SerialFlowWriter
extends Object

 批量序列化写入器(需配合读取器使用).
        用于把多个内存对象写到外存的同一个序列化文件.
 
 使用示例:
        SerialFlowWriter sfw = new SerialFlowWriter(FILE_PATH, true);
        while(true) {
                sfw.write(obj);
                // .....
        }
        sfw.flush();
 
        sfw.write(obj2);
        sfw.write(obj3);
        sfw.close();
